copyDTEdge

public static DTEdge copyDTEdge(DTEdge oldEdge,
                                Map<String,DTNode> existing,
                                DependencyTreeTransformer dt,
                                DTNode source)
                         throws NameAlreadyBoundException
Copies the given edge and creates a new one. Also copies the target node, checking if it already has been copied in the the HashMap. Adds the new edge to the given DependencyTree.

Parameters:
oldEdge - The edge to be copied
existing - HashMap with copied nodes
dt - DependencyTreeTransformer containing all copies
source - Source node of the new edge
Returns:
The new DTEdge
Throws:
NameAlreadyBoundException - very unlikely
